9713 int
9714 chksum_insert_repl_log_and_demote_table_lock (REPL_INFO * repl_info, const OID * class_oidp)
9715 {
9716 #if defined(CS_MODE)
9717  int req_error, success = ER_FAILED;
9718  int request_size = 0, strlen1, strlen2, strlen3, strlen4;
9719  char *request = NULL, *ptr;

9722  REPL_INFO_SBR *repl_stmt;
9723 
9724  reply = OR_ALIGNED_BUF_START (a_reply);
9725 
9726  switch (repl_info->repl_info_type)
9727  {
9728  case REPL_INFO_TYPE_SBR:
9729  repl_stmt = (REPL_INFO_SBR *) repl_info->info;
9730  request_size = (OR_OID_SIZE /* class oid */
9731  + OR_INT_SIZE /* REPL_INFO.REPL_INFO_TYPE */
9732  + OR_INT_SIZE /* REPL_INFO_SCHEMA.statement_type */

9737

9739  if (request == NULL)
9740  {
9741  er_set (ER_ERROR_SEVERITY, ARG_FILE_LINE, ER_OUT_OF_VIRTUAL_MEMORY, 1, (size_t) request_size);
9742  return ER_FAILED;
9743  }
9744 
9745  ptr = or_pack_oid (request, class_oidp);
9746  ptr = or_pack_int (ptr, REPL_INFO_TYPE_SBR);
9747  ptr = or_pack_int (ptr, repl_stmt->statement_type);
9748  ptr = pack_const_string_with_length (ptr, repl_stmt->name, strlen1);
9749  ptr = pack_const_string_with_length (ptr, repl_stmt->stmt_text, strlen2);
9750  ptr = pack_const_string_with_length (ptr, repl_stmt->db_user, strlen3);
9751  ptr = pack_const_string_with_length (ptr, repl_stmt->sys_prm_context, strlen4);
9752  req_error =
9753  net_client_request (NET_SERVER_CHKSUM_REPL, request, request_size, reply, OR_ALIGNED_BUF_SIZE (a_reply),
9754  NULL, 0, NULL, 0);
9755  if (!req_error)
9756  {
9757  or_unpack_int (reply, &success);
9758  }
9759 
9760  free_and_init (request);
9761  break;
9762 
9763  default:
9764  break;
9765  }
9766 
9767  return success;
9768 #else /* CS_MODE */
9769  int r = ER_FAILED;
9770 
9771  THREAD_ENTRY *thread_p = enter_server ();
9772 
9773  r = xchksum_insert_repl_log_and_demote_table_lock (thread_p, repl_info, class_oidp);

9775  exit_server (*thread_p);
9776

9778 #endif /* !CS_MODE */

9841 /*
9842  * locator_redistribute_partition_data () - redistribute partition data
9843  *
9844  * return : error code
9845  *
9846  * thread_p (in) :
9847  * class_oid (in) : parent class OID
9848  * no_oids (in) : number of OIDs in the list (promoted partitions)
9849  * oid_list (in) : partition OID list (promoted partitions)
9850  */
9851 int
9852 locator_redistribute_partition_data (OID * class_oid, int no_oids, OID * oid_list)
9853 {
9854 #if defined(CS_MODE)
9855  int success = ER_FAILED, req_error;
9856  char *request, *reply, *ptr;
9857  int request_size = 0;
9858  int i;
9859  OR_ALIGNED_BUF (OR_INT_SIZE) a_reply;
9860 
9861  reply = OR_ALIGNED_BUF_START (a_reply);
9862 
9863  if (oid_list == NULL || no_oids < 1)
9864  {
9865  return ER_QPROC_INVALID_PARAMETER;
9866  }
9867 
9868  request_size = OR_OID_SIZE + OR_INT_SIZE + no_oids * OR_OID_SIZE;
9869 
9870  request = (char *) malloc (request_size);
9871  if (request == NULL)
9872  {
9873  er_set (ER_ERROR_SEVERITY, ARG_FILE_LINE, ER_OUT_OF_VIRTUAL_MEMORY, 1, (size_t) request_size);
9874  return ER_OUT_OF_VIRTUAL_MEMORY;
9875  }
9876 
9877  ptr = request;
9878  ptr = or_pack_oid (ptr, class_oid);
9879  ptr = or_pack_int (ptr, no_oids);
9880 
9881  for (i = 0; i < no_oids; i++)
9882  {
9883  ptr = or_pack_oid (ptr, &oid_list[i]);
9884  }
9885 
9886  req_error =
9887  net_client_request (NET_SERVER_LC_REDISTRIBUTE_PARTITION_DATA, request, request_size, reply,
9888  OR_ALIGNED_BUF_SIZE (a_reply), NULL, 0, NULL, 0);
9889  if (!req_error)
9890  {
9891  ptr = or_unpack_int (reply, &success);
9892  }
9893 
9894  free_and_init (request);
9895 
9896  return success;
9897 
9898 #else /* CS_MODE */
9899  int success = ER_FAILED;
9900 
9901  THREAD_ENTRY *thread_p = enter_server ();
9902 
9903  success = xlocator_redistribute_partition_data (thread_p, class_oid, no_oids, oid_list);
9904 
9905  exit_server (*thread_p);
9906 
9907  return success;
9908 #endif /* !CS_MODE */
9909 }

9911 /*
9912  * netcl_spacedb () - client-side function to get database space info
9913  *
9914  * return : error code
9915  * spaceall (out) : output aggregated space information
9916  * spacevols (out) : if not NULL, output space information per volume
9917  * spacefiles (out) : if not NULL, out detailed space information on file usage
9918  */
9919 int
9920 netcl_spacedb (SPACEDB_ALL * spaceall, SPACEDB_ONEVOL ** spacevols, SPACEDB_FILES * spacefiles)
9921 {
9922 #if defined (CS_MODE)
9923  int error_code = NO_ERROR;
9924  OR_ALIGNED_BUF (2 * OR_INT_SIZE) a_request;
9925  char *request;
9926  OR_ALIGNED_BUF (2 * OR_INT_SIZE) a_reply;
9927  char *reply;
9928  char *data_reply = NULL;
9929  int data_reply_size = 0;
9930  char *ptr;
9931 
9932  request = OR_ALIGNED_BUF_START (a_request);
9933  reply = OR_ALIGNED_BUF_START (a_reply);
9934 
9935  ptr = or_pack_int (request, spacevols != NULL ? 1 : 0);
9936  ptr = or_pack_int (ptr, spacefiles != NULL ? 1 : 0);
9937 
9938  error_code = net_client_request2 (NET_SERVER_SPACEDB, request, OR_ALIGNED_BUF_SIZE (a_request), reply,
9939  OR_ALIGNED_BUF_SIZE (a_reply), NULL, 0, &data_reply, &data_reply_size);
9940  if (error_code != NO_ERROR)
9941  {
9942  assert (data_reply == NULL);
9943  return error_code;
9944  }
9945  ptr = or_unpack_int (reply, &data_reply_size);
9946  ptr = or_unpack_int (ptr, &error_code);
9947  if (error_code != NO_ERROR)
9948  {
9949  /* error */
9950  ASSERT_ERROR ();
9951  return error_code;
9952  }
9953  if (data_reply == NULL)
9954  {
9955  assert_release (false);
9956  return ER_FAILED;
9957  }
9958  ptr = or_unpack_spacedb (data_reply, spaceall, spacevols, spacefiles);
9959  if (ptr == NULL)
9960  {
9961  ASSERT_ERROR_AND_SET (error_code);
9962  return error_code;
9963  }
9964  assert ((ptr - data_reply) == data_reply_size);
9965 
9966  free_and_init (data_reply);
9967  return NO_ERROR;
9968 
9969 #else /* !CS_MODE */ /* SA_MDOE */
9970  int error_code = ER_FAILED;
9971 
9972  THREAD_ENTRY *thread_p = enter_server ();
9973  error_code = disk_spacedb (thread_p, spaceall, spacevols);
9974  if (error_code != NO_ERROR)
9975  {
9976  ASSERT_ERROR ();
9977  }
9978  else if (spacefiles != NULL)
9979  {
9980  error_code = file_spacedb (thread_p, spacefiles);
9981  if (error_code != NO_ERROR)
9982  {
9983  ASSERT_ERROR ();
9984  }
9985  }
9986  exit_server (*thread_p);
9987 
9988  return error_code;
9989 #endif /* SA_MODE */
9990 }
